When adding mobile FFI functions:
- Add Rust implementation in src/mobile_ffi/ffi.rs with #[no_mangle]
- Include JSON serialization via serde_json
- Provide memory management (arxos_free_string)
- Update Swift wrapper in ios/ArxOSMobile/Services/ArxOSCoreFFI.swift
- Update Kotlin wrapper in android/app/src/main/java/com/arxos/mobile/
